[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 185     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m | **Encryption** | S3: SSE-KMS; Redshift: encrypted cluster with KMS CMK; SageMaker: volume encryption and inter-container encryption; QuickSight: TLS in transit |
