[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      190[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | **VPC** | Production: Redshift in private subnet, SageMaker jobs in VPC mode with VPC endpoints for S3 and SageMaker API (endpoint policies restricting to specific buckets and APIs), Glue connections through VPC, QuickSight VPC connection for Redshift access |
[0m[49m[39m  187, 191[0m:[39m[49m | **CloudTrail** | Enabled for all service API calls. Provider profiling data is sensitive; full audit trail required. |
